        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1613303253" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6915888864722622606">Beautiful writing. The story begins with a Chinese young man going to Japan to recover from a serious illness during the war with China. The slow pace about everyday activities while he is being cared for by a Japanese caretaker is meditative. I love learning about other cultures and history. Definitely recommend.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


