          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/16070942-the-samurai-s-garden">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56491386-kirsty?shelf=january-2017">january-2017</a>
